<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:15:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大众汽车第三季度交付量下降，确认欧洲汽车行业面临的挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-q3-deliveries-down-confirming-challenges-european-auto-sector-2024-10-11/</link><description>大众汽车集团周五公布第三季度全球交付量下降 7%，显示出欧洲汽车行业面临的挑战有多大。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-q3-deliveries-down-confirming-challenges-european-auto-sector-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>央行机构呼吁更详细地监控银行流动性风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/central-bank-body-calls-more-detailed-monitoring-bank-liquidity-risks-2024-10-11/</link><description>国际清算银行周五在对去年银行业动荡的研究中表示，银行监管机构应确保全球银行的各个实体拥有充足的流动性，而不仅仅是监控集团层面的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 08:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/central-bank-body-calls-more-detailed-monitoring-bank-liquidity-risks-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>两名涉嫌策划 2021 年袭击中国人的巴基斯坦武装分子在枪战中丧生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-suspected-pakistani-militants-behind-2021-attack-chinese-killed-shootout-2024-10-11/</link><description>反恐官员称，两名参与 2021 年袭击、造成 9 名中国工程师死亡的武装分子周五在巴基斯坦中部地区的一次枪战中被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-suspected-pakistani-militants-behind-2021-attack-chinese-killed-shootout-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国刺激计划的不确定性影响欧洲股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-stocks-dip-china-caution-sets-french-markets-lag-2024-10-11/</link><description>由于紧张的投资者等待中国刺激计划的最新消息，欧洲股市周五下跌，而法国股市在政府公布旨在解决不断上升的财政赤字的 2025 年预算后小幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:24:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-stocks-dip-china-caution-sets-french-markets-lag-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷9个月中国销量下滑三分之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-nine-month-china-sales-plunge-by-third-2024-10-11/</link><description>德国跑车制造商保时捷周五公布，其在中国的 9 个月销量下降了 29%，与宝马和梅赛德斯一样，其在中国的业绩也表现疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsches-nine-month-china-sales-plunge-by-third-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于节日吸引买家，亚洲黄金印度价格在两个月后出现溢价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-prices-premium-after-two-months-festive-season-draws-buyers-2024-10-11/</link><description>印度实物黄金交易商本周两个月来首次收取溢价，原因是即将到来的节日季吸引了一些金饰购买，而疲软的消费者信心抑制了中国节后的需求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:46:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-prices-premium-after-two-months-festive-season-draws-buyers-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>巴克莱银行：中国股市每周资金流入创历史新高，日本股市出现20年来最大流出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-equities-see-record-weekly-inflows-japan-has-biggest-outflow-20-years-2024-10-11/</link><description>巴克莱援引 EPFR 的数据表示，截至周三的一周，新兴市场股票的资金流入创历史新高，其中中国股市的资金流入创纪录。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-equities-see-record-weekly-inflows-japan-has-biggest-outflow-20-years-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>土耳其对中国、俄罗斯、印度、日本进口钢铁征收反倾销税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-imposes-anti-dumping-duties-steel-imports-china-russia-india-japan-2024-10-11/</link><description>根据周五官方公报公布的决定，土耳其对来自中国、俄罗斯、印度和日本的部分进口钢材征收反倾销税，其中对中国进口钢材征收的关税最高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 05:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-imposes-anti-dumping-duties-steel-imports-china-russia-india-japan-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>高夫在武汉公开赛四分之一决赛中击败利内特获得今年第50场胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/gauff-beats-linette-wuhan-open-quarter-finals-earn-50th-win-year-2024-10-11/</link><description>世界排名第四的可可·高芙在周五的武汉公开赛四分之一决赛中以 6-0 6-4 击败玛格达·利内特，赢得了她今年在 WTA 正赛中的第 50 场胜利，有可能在半决赛中与顶级选手展开对决种子阿琳娜·萨巴伦卡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 05:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/gauff-beats-linette-wuhan-open-quarter-finals-earn-50th-win-year-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚教练波波维奇在日本测试前看到了更多变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-coach-popovic-sees-more-changes-before-japan-test-2024-10-11/</link><description>澳大利亚队主教练托尼·波波维奇在上任之初就以一场令人鼓舞的战胜中国队的比赛开始，他预计对阵日本队的世界杯预选赛任务将会发生变化。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 02:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-coach-popovic-sees-more-changes-before-japan-test-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>股市横盘整理，等待中国的刺激举措</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-11/</link><description>周五，全球股市横盘整理，原因是中国股市惊人的涨势暂停，投资者在北京本周末公布备受期待的财政刺激政策更新之前不愿加大押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 01:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-11/</guid></item><item><title>李克强希望日中双方相向而行，推动两国关系沿着正确轨道发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-japan-can-meet-it-halfway-keep-relations-right-track-says-chinese-2024-10-10/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国总理李强表示，在两国努力缓解该地区不断升级的紧张局势之际，他希望日本能够与中国相向而行，使双边关系保持在正确的轨道上。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 23:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-japan-can-meet-it-halfway-keep-relations-right-track-says-chinese-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国通胀、中国计划谨慎； BOK 设置切割</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 21:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>西尔弗表示，在争议之后他预计NBA比赛将重返中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</link><description>亚当·萧华 (Adam Silver) 专员认为，在香港民主抗议引发的争议引发对北美顶级联赛的强烈抵制五年后，NBA 可能会再次在中国举办比赛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普以汽车贷款税收减免和中国镇压来吸引汽车工人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周四提议对汽车贷款利息实行免税，并阻止中国汽车制造商在美国销售汽车，以期在竞选活动的最后几周吸引汽车工人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>